OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774195867
OL,3,CFootball fan given three-year ban over
OL,4,Cracist and homophobic social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FAn Everton supporter has been handed a
OL,8,Fthree-year football banning order
OL,9,Fafter admitting to posting racist,
OL,10,Fhomophobic and transphobic messages on
OL,11,Fsocial media.
OL,13,FFrancis Fleming, 44, of Liverpool,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to 10 offences of
OL,15,Fsending malicious communications, at
OL,16,FSefton Magistrates' Court on Thursday
OL,17,F19 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
