PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774195867
OL,3,CFootball fan given three-year ban over
OL,4,Cracist and homophobic social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FThe offences related to a series of
OL,8,Fsocial media posts made between 2023
OL,9,Fand 2024, the majority of which were
OL,10,Flinked to football.
OL,12,FThe activity was reported by Everton
OL,13,FFC after the club became aware of the
OL,14,Fcontent online.
OL,16,FIn addition to the banning order,
OL,17,FFleming was given a community order
OL,18,Fand ordered to pay fines.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774195867
OL,3,CFootball fan given three-year ban over
OL,4,Cracist and homophobic social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FMerseyside Police Detective Constable
OL,8,FTom Sharrocks said the case should
OL,9,Fserve as a warning to others.
OL,11,FHe said: "I hope this result shows
OL,12,Fthat people can't hide behind their
OL,13,Fsocial media accounts and post racist,
OL,14,Fhomophobic and transphobic comments
OL,15,Fonline.
OL,17,F"This will never be accepted and it's
OL,18,Fpleasing that Fleming is now subjected
OL,19,Fto a three-year football banning order
OL,20,Ffor his appalling behaviour.
OL,26,@sD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
