FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774195867
OL,3,CFootball fan given three-year ban over
OL,4,Cracist and homophobic social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,F"Merseyside Police will continue to
OL,8,Fwork alongside our local clubs and the
OL,9,FKick It Out campaign to identify and
OL,10,Fbring to justice anyone found
OL,11,Fresponsible for committing a hate
OL,12,Fcrime whether it's inside a stadium or
OL,13,Fon social media.
OL,15,F"I hope this sends a clear message and
OL,16,Facts as a deterrent to others that we
OL,17,Fwill put you before the courts to be
OL,18,Fprosecuted if you choose to behave in
OL,19,Fsuch a deplorable way."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
